I'm compiling for iOS which I think is the difference here. I did find references to a similar issue for Android that was resolved some time ago, but no references to selective registration working (or failing) on iOS.

As mentioned above [my ops_to_register.h is available on Dropbox](https://www.dropbox.com/s/bginmeuipl5i479/ops_to_register.h?dl=0) It compiles fine but fails at runtime, with an error staying there is no OpKernel for Conv2D.
